reviewText: I couldn't stop laughing. It was so funny!!!
This show will have you in tears this show is so funny it is hilarious Kevin Hart is the most funniest dude ever
I never even knew this was on tv so when i seen this on amazon and a fan of Kevin Heart I just had to have it. I must say this is the only thing he has done that I didn't like.
It was funny. Not a Kevin Hart anymore but my godson enjoyed it.

Although nothing really stands out in this series, it isn't by any means a bad show.  The actors did a good job with the material and given time and perhaps a different network the show would have found it's footing.
